      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, providing a reliable driving experience. While the exterior and interior are generally clean, there are a few minor cosmetic blemishes, such as light scratches and minimal upholstery wear, consistent with regular use. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for the road.",
