    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, preserved in showroom condition. This specimen exhibits an unblemished aesthetic and rigorous mechanical integrity, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From the flawless paintwork to the pristine interior appointments, every detail adheres to the highest standards of automotive excellence. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this rare example of collector-grade quality, which represents the pinnacle of its class in both form and function.",
