    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s in pristine, showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve truly babied this car from day one and kept it tucked away in a garage. No scratches, no spills, and it still has that fresh new-car feel! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. You really have to see it in person to see how perfect it is. Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
