    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Offering a pristine example of automotive engineering, maintained to a concours standard. This specimen features a high-revving, naturally aspirated powerplant with a razor-sharp throttle response and a perfectly synchronized close-ratio manual transmission. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. Every mechanical component, from the multi-piston monoblock calipers to the forged alloy wheels, exhibits zero thermal fatigue or oxidative wear. A true turn-key investment for the discerning driver seeking peak mechanical purity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
