      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "2022 model. Mint condition. Garage kept. Smoke-free interior. Zero accidents. Full service history available. Clean title. Professional inspections welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in GT Silver Metallic, maintained to a standard that defines 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been strictly garage-kept under a custom breathable cover and has never been driven in inclement weather. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like luster. Inside, the Black leather interior remains in showroom state; the seat bolsters show zero compression or wear, and the cabin retains its original factory scent. Every surface, from the Alcantara headliner to the brushed aluminum trim, is completely unmarked. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete service history exclusively performed by authorized technicians. The staggered 20-inch Carrera S wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in high-performance rubber with near-full tread depth. This is an investment-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
